    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows some noticeable scratches, a few minor dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all electronics and the air conditioning still function properly. Mechanically, the car starts right up and runs well, though it may soon require some routine maintenance like new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has served me well but definitely shows its age and mileage.",
      "price": 21500.0,
