    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and retains its original factory luster. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero paint chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear, and the original 'new car' scent persists. Every electronic component and switch functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive folder of service records from authorized dealerships. With incredibly low mileage and a clean history, this is the closest you can get to buying a brand-new model from the showroom floor. No modifications, no stories\u2014just pure, unadulterated excellence for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive engineering, this vehicle is offered in impeccable condition. Meticulously preserved and showing virtually no signs of previous ownership, it represents the absolute pinnacle of its class. For the discerning professional who demands aesthetic perfection and mechanical integrity, this unit offers an unrivaled acquisition opportunity. A rare find maintained to the highest standards of excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
