      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this car\u2014it is an absolute dream and in truly flawless condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and honestly still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. If you're looking for something that drives like brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
