    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S represents the pinnacle of the wide-body naturally aspirated 911s. Powered by a 3.6L flat-six featuring VarioCam Plus, the engine delivers linear power through a precise G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The all-wheel-drive system provides exceptional mechanical grip, while the Turbo-derived chassis and braking system\u2014featuring 4-piston monobloc calipers\u2014ensure track-ready deceleration. This example is in showroom condition, featuring a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a clean DME over-rev report. The suspension remains taut with factory-spec damping, and the underbody is free of any fluid seepage. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
